columns.name: name
columns.description: The name of the build project.

columns.name: arn
columns.description: The Amazon Resource Name (ARN) of the build project.

columns.name: description
columns.description: A description that makes the build project easy to identify.

columns.name: concurrent_build_limit
columns.description: The maximum number of concurrent builds that are allowed for this project.

columns.name: created
columns.description: When the build project was created, expressed in Unix time format.

columns.name: last_modified
columns.description: When the build project's settings were last modified, expressed in Unix time format.

columns.name: encryption_key
columns.description: The AWS Key Management Service (AWS KMS) customer master key (CMK) to be.

columns.name: queued_timeout_in_minutes
columns.description: The number of minutes a build is allowed to be queued before it times out.

columns.name: service_role
columns.description: The ARN of the AWS Identity and Access Management (IAM) role that enables AWS CodeBuild to interact with dependent AWS services on behalf of the AWS account.

columns.name: source_version
columns.description: A version of the build input to be built for this project.

columns.name: timeout_in_minutes
columns.description: How long, in minutes, from 5 to 480 (8 hours), for AWS CodeBuild to wait before timing out any related build that did not get marked as completed.

columns.name: artifacts
columns.description: Information about the build output artifacts for the build project.

columns.name: badge
columns.description: Information about the build badge for the build project.

columns.name: build_batch_config
columns.description: A ProjectBuildBatchConfig object that defines the batch build options for the project.

columns.name: cache
columns.description: Information about the cache for the build project.

columns.name: environment
columns.description: Information about the build environment for this build project.

columns.name: file_system_locations
columns.description: An array of ProjectFileSystemLocation objects for a CodeBuild build project.

columns.name: logs_config
columns.description: Information about logs for the build project. A project can create logs in Amazon CloudWatch Logs, an S3 bucket or both.

columns.name: project_visibility
columns.description: Visibility of the build project.

columns.name: secondary_artifacts
columns.description: An array of ProjectArtifacts objects.

columns.name: secondary_source_versions
columns.description: An array of ProjectSource objects.

columns.name: secondary_sources
columns.description: An array of ProjectSource objects.

columns.name: source
columns.description: Information about the build input source code for this build project.

columns.name: vpc_config
columns.description: Information about the VPC configuration that AWS CodeBuild accesses.

columns.name: webhook
columns.description: Information about a webhook that connects repository events to a build project in AWS CodeBuild.

columns.name: tags_src
columns.description: A list of tag key and value pairs associated with this build project.
